title: Football Friday In KELOLAND
text:
October 9, 2015, 6:10 AM SIOUX FALLS, SD - 
Football players across KELOLAND will hit the fields again Friday for another week of high school football. 
Watch 11AA #3 Brookings at 11AA #2 Mitchell on our livestream at 7 p.m. 
The KELOLAND Sports Team will have highlights of 10 other games across KELOLAND on the KELOLAND SportsZone following the 10 p.m news. 
11A Vermillion @ 11A #4 Sioux Falls Christian (Game of the Week) 11AAA #1 Roosevelt @ 11AAA #4 Brandon Valley 11AAA #2 Washington @ 11AAA Watertown 11AAA #3 O'Gorman @ 11AAA Rapid City Stevens 11AAA Rapid City Central @ 11AAA #5 Lincoln 11AA #4 Brookings @ 11AA #2 Mitchell 11A #1 Madison @ 11A Canton 11A Tea Area @ 11A #3 West Central 7a 9B #4 Alcester-Hudson @ 9A #1 Canistota 9B #1 Langford Area @ 9AA Ipswich/Edmunds Central Iowa --- Unity Christian @ West Lyon 
We want to see what you see at the games. Share your pictures and videos with us by emailing ushare@keloland.com; submitting a photo using the KELOLAND News App ; upload it to the uShare Photo Gallery ; or use #kelosports when you post on Facebook, Twitter or Instagram. Sports Resources
